VLN'yMY MYD'y L'aYShH 'aYSh GBVUr ChYL MMShPhChTh 'aLYMLK VShMV B'yZ.
VTh'aMUr UrVTh HMV'aBYH 'aL-N'yMY 'aLKH-N'a HShDH V'aLQTH BShBLYM 'aChUr 'aShUr 'aMTSh'a-ChN B'yYNYV VTh'aMUr LH LKY BThY.
VThLK VThBV'a VThLQT BShDH 'aChUrY HQTShUrYM VYQUr MQUrH ChLQTh HShDH LB'yZ 'aShUr MMShPhChTh 'aLYMLK.
VHNH-B'yZ B'a MBYTh LChM VY'aMUr LQVTShUrYM YHVH 'yMKM VY'aMUrV LV YBUrKK YHVH.
VY'aMUr B'yZ LN'yUrV HNTShB 'yL-HQVTShUrYM LMY HN'yUrH HZ'aTh.
VY'yN HN'yUr HNTShB 'yL-HQVTShUrYM VY'aMUr N'yUrH MV'aBYH HY'a HShBH 'yM-N'yMY MShDH MV'aB.
VTh'aMUr 'aLQTH-N'a V'aSPhThY B'yMUrYM 'aChUrY HQVTShUrYM VThBV'a VTh'yMVD M'aZ HBQUr V'yD-'yThH ZH ShBThH HBYTh M'yT.
VY'aMUr B'yZ 'aL-UrVTh HLV'a ShM'yTh BThY 'aL-ThLKY LLQT BShDH 'aChUr VGM L'a Th'yBVUrY MZH VKH ThDBQYN 'yM-N'yUrThY.
'yYNYK BShDH 'aShUr-YQTShUrVN VHLKTh 'aChUrYHN HLV'a TShVYThY 'aTh-HN'yUrYM LBLThY NG'yK VTShMTh VHLKTh 'aL-HKLYM VShThYTh M'aShUr YSh'aBVN HN'yUrYM.
VThPhL 'yL-PhNYH VThShThChV 'aUrTShH VTh'aMUr 'aLYV MDV'y MTSh'aThY ChN B'yYNYK LHKYUrNY V'aNKY NKUrYH.
VY'yN B'yZ VY'aMUr LH HGD HGD LY KL 'aShUr-'yShYTh 'aTh-ChMVThK 'aChUrY MVTh 'aYShK VTh'yZBY 'aBYK V'aMK V'aUrTSh MVLDThK VThLKY 'aL-'yM 'aShUr L'a-YD'yTh ThMVL ShLShVM.
YShLM YHVH Ph'yLK VThHY MShKUrThK ShLMH M'yM YHVH 'aLHY YShUr'aL 'aShUr-B'aTh LChSVTh ThChTh-KNPhYV.
VTh'aMUr 'aMTSh'a-ChN B'yYNYK 'aDNY KY NChMThNY VKY DBUrTh 'yL-LB ShPhChThK V'aNKY L'a 'aHYH K'aChTh ShPhChThYK.
VY'aMUr LH B'yZ L'yTh H'aKL GShY HLM V'aKLTh MN-HLChM VTBLTh PhThK BChMTSh VThShB MTShD HQVTShUrYM VYTShBT-LH QLY VTh'aKL VThShB'y VThThUr.
VThQM LLQT VYTShV B'yZ 'aTh-N'yUrYV L'aMUr GM BYN H'yMUrYM ThLQT VL'a ThKLYMVH.
VGM ShL-ThShLV LH MN-HTShBThYM V'yZBThM VLQTH VL'a ThG'yUrV-BH.
VThLQT BShDH 'yD-H'yUrB VThChBT 'aTh 'aShUr-LQTH VYHY K'aYPhH Sh'yUrYM.
VThSh'a VThBV'a H'yYUr VThUr'a ChMVThH 'aTh 'aShUr-LQTH VThVTSh'a VThThN-LH 'aTh 'aShUr- HVThUrH MShB'yH.
VTh'aMUr LH ChMVThH 'aYPhH LQTTh HYVM V'aNH 'yShYTh YHY MKYUrK BUrVK VThGD LChMVThH 'aTh 'aShUr-'yShThH 'yMV VTh'aMUr ShM H'aYSh 'aShUr 'yShYThY 'yMV HYVM B'yZ.
